<a href="https://www.uhasselt.be/en/instituten-en/dsi"><img src="dsi_logo.png" width="200" style="float:right"/></a>

Professor, <a href="http://www.uhasselt.be">Universiteit Hasselt</a>,
<a href="http://alpha.uhasselt.be/research/groups/theocomp/">databases &amp; theoretical
computer science group</a>

