<hr>
I chaired the Executive Committee of
<a href="https://databasetheory.org/PODS">PODS</a> for the editions
<a href="http://sigmod2017.org">2017</a> and
<a href="http://sigmod2018.org">2018</a>.
<p>
From 2001 until March 2011 I served as chair of the
<a href="https://databasetheory.org/icdt-pages">ICDT</a>
Council.  The current chair is Dan Olteanu.

